47:19.999 --> 47:22.667
özellikle hindistancevizi ağaçları,

47:22.667 --> 47:25.291
hepsi denize doğru viraj

47:26.208 --> 47:29.083
Çünkü deniz onlara bu uzmanlığı verdi.

47:29.083 --> 47:32.917
Hindistan cevizindeki su denizden geliyor.

47:32.917 --> 47:37.917
Yani hepsinde bu saygı var.

47:38.208 --> 47:40.917
denize karşı alçakgönüllülük.

47:41.208 --> 47:47.458
Aynı şekilde suçlu olmayan bir kişi

47:47.999 --> 47:50.667
sadece gerçekten mütevazi olacak

47:50.917 --> 47:52.667
çünkü dediğim gibi, suçlu insanlar

47:52.917 --> 47:56.875
iğnelemeleri, iğrenç sözleriyle saldırgan,

47:56.875 --> 47:59.709
cevaplarını vererek, açıklamalarıyla.

48:00.000 --> 48:06.792
Ama mütevazi bir insan özgür bir insandır.

48:07.208 --> 48:08.917
mütevazi olmakta özgür

48:09.333 --> 48:12.333
nazik olmakta özgür

48:12.792 --> 48:15.000
nazik olmak, şefkatli olmak.

48:15.291 --> 48:19.792
Ve bu tür bir Sahaja Yogi olmak zorundasın.

48:20.083 --> 48:21.750
Böylece insanlar seninle tanıştığında

48:21.750 --> 48:23.333
alçakgönüllülüğünden etkilendiler.

48:23.583 --> 48:27.709
Ancak alçakgönüllülüğün hiçbir önemi yoktur.

48:28.083 --> 48:30.917
- masumiyet ve alçakgönüllülük.

48:32.542 --> 48:35.999
Ben, bu kaliteden tamamen mahrumum.

48:36.333 --> 48:37.792
Mütevazi olamam,

48:38.125 --> 48:40.291
ve beni asla alçakgönüllü olmaya çalışmamalısın

48:40.291 --> 48:42.333
çünkü bu yapılmayacak.

48:43.000 --> 48:48.500
Ama kimse Benimle karşılaştığında davranışımda söyleyemez

48:48.500 --> 48:50.375
alçakgönüllü değilim.

48:50.750 --> 48:53.959
Çok mütevazi biri olarak davranıyorum.

48:54.709 --> 48:58.625
Çok mütevazi bir insan olarak hareket edebilirim ama çok dürüst olmak gerekirse,

48:58.875 --> 49:02.750
I have no humility of any kind within Me, no humility.

49:03.000 --> 49:06.291
Compassion is very different from humility.

49:06.625 --> 49:09.500
Humility is a human quality,

49:09.834 --> 49:13.709
is a special quality only the bhaktas have.

49:14.291 --> 49:17.875
Only the bhaktas have, it's such a beautiful quality

49:18.500 --> 49:21.834
of taking the showers of bliss.

49:22.834 --> 49:25.959
The one who gives bliss cannot be humble

49:25.959 --> 49:28.041
because it cannot take anything.

49:28.291 --> 49:32.125
It's the only human beings who are humble,

49:32.375 --> 49:35.875
and who can take it and achieve it and receive it.

49:36.125 --> 49:42.166
And the person who cannot take is so lonely, so lonely.

49:42.709 --> 49:47.875
Such a person cannot get companionship with anyone,

49:48.250 --> 49:50.750
because it has to give, and give, and give.

49:50.750 --> 49:57.291
It's so lonely, and has to face everything oneself.

49:57.583 --> 50:01.291
Those who are humble can only become friendly

50:01.291 --> 50:05.750
with each other, can share their problems with each other.

50:06.000 --> 50:10.041
I cannot, because you have no solutions.

50:10.750 --> 50:12.959
I have to solve My own problem.

50:13.250 --> 50:18.291
So the humility can only help you to articulate

50:18.583 --> 50:20.583
and to have rapport with your friends,

50:20.834 --> 50:23.500
everyone, share your difficulties.

50:23.834 --> 50:26.583
But again I have to warn you because it always happens,

50:26.875 --> 50:30.041
your humility should not be sympathetic.

50:31.625 --> 50:34.166
Humility is a detached person,

50:34.166 --> 50:36.375
it's a detached quality.

50:36.625 --> 50:39.500
It's not a quality that gets attached

50:39.500 --> 50:41.500
to one person or second person.

50:42.250 --> 50:44.417
It's a humble style of life

50:44.417 --> 50:46.709
where you are not arrogant unnecessarily,

50:46.959 --> 50:48.709
you don't shout at people.

50:49.000 --> 50:52.625
But in India we say the cow

50:52.959 --> 50:54.583
is a very humble animal.

50:54.834 --> 50:56.625
It gives its milk,

50:57.375 --> 50:59.333
it provides everything,

50:59.583 --> 51:01.500
it doesn't attack anyone.

51:03.333 --> 51:06.583
So humility is such a guard for you.

51:07.291 --> 51:09.792
Of course, sometimes people take advantage of humble people,

51:10.000 --> 51:10.625
doesn't matter.

51:10.625 --> 51:13.208
As long as you have not lost your humility,

51:13.458 --> 51:14.333
everything is all right.

51:14.667 --> 51:16.166
But people lose their humility.

51:16.166 --> 51:17.667
When people try to trouble them

51:17.667 --> 51:19.208
they become left-Vishuddhites

51:19.208 --> 51:22.417
and then they lose their humility,

51:22.792 --> 51:24.917
and that's one thing one should not lose;

51:25.417 --> 51:29.291
because if you have to keep connection with the Divine

51:29.625 --> 51:31.875
then you have to be humble.

51:32.208 --> 51:33.917
Başka yol yok.

51:34.417 --> 51:36.542
If you are not a humble person

51:37.041 --> 51:38.875
you cannot keep the relationship.

51:39.208 --> 51:42.999
See, two qualities, like a plug and the socket.

51:43.291 --> 51:45.166
The plug has to be the plug,

51:45.417 --> 51:47.458
the socket has to be socket.

51:47.458 --> 51:49.458
In the same way if you have to

51:49.750 --> 51:52.333
get something out of the Divine,

51:52.333 --> 51:54.166
you have to be humble people.

51:54.166 --> 51:57.208
Through arrogance you will not get anything,

51:57.625 --> 52:00.417
through aggression you'll not get anything,

52:00.999 --> 52:03.291
through anything .& Some people also feel that

52:03.291 --> 52:06.667
