53:37.750 --> 53:39.959
"Am I a very forward type of a person,

53:39.959 --> 53:41.625
do I go forward all the time?

53:41.625 --> 53:44.999
Do I sit all the time before everybody else?

53:45.250 --> 53:47.083
Do I try to be arrogant to Mother?

53:47.083 --> 53:48.875
Do I say "no" to Mother?

53:48.875 --> 53:50.083
Do I behave like?"

53:50.083 --> 53:51.500
And see all these points within yourself.

53:51.500 --> 53:53.959
It's not for others, it's for you to see,

53:54.250 --> 53:55.375
"How far I go?

53:55.667 --> 54:00.333
